WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Start with the visible benchmark area. If no benchmark has been run, the tool says so plainly.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Use this as a reviewed revenue signal that points attention to where money may be leaking.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:22.000
RGS may ask for stronger evidence before the read becomes useful enough to act on.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Look for the recommended next inspection, then decide what should be reviewed before action.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:34.000
This improves visibility. It does not guarantee revenue recovery, clean data, or a specific outcome.

